comments: Wright (WAS) has a hand on the ball and when Siakam (TOR) brings it forward, he makes incidental contact with Siakam's hand on the ball.
VanVleet (TOR) lowers his arm to contest Beal's (WAS) shot attempt near the basket and marginal contact occurs.
Wright (WAS) remains in bounds as he controls the rebound.
Poeltl (TOR) and Porzingis (WAS) mutually engage and immediately disengage as marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Anunoby (TOR) jumps vertically and absorbs the contact initiated by Wright (WAS) during the driving shot attempt.
VanVleet's (TOR) shot attempt goes out of bounds.
VanVleet (TOR) reaches in and makes clean contact with the ball, briefly dislodging it from Beal (WAS).
Trent Jr. (TOR) and Anunoby (TOR) legally contest Beal's (WAS) driving shot attempt.
VanVleet (TOR) reaches in and makes clean contact with the ball during Beal's (WAS) driving shot attempt.
Wright (WAS) moves along with Siakam (TOR) on his path to the basket and marginal contact occurs that does not impact his SQBR.
Siakam (TOR) legally contests Kuzma's (WAS) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Siakam (TOR) extends his off-arm into Kuzma (WAS) and dislodges him from his defensive position.
Marginal contact occurs between Anunoby (TOR) and Wright (WAS) as the screen is set and Wright is not dislodged from his screening position.
Replay review of the foul called on Siakam (TOR) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful.  Siakam initiates arm and body contact to Kuzma (WAS), affecting his driving shot attempt.
Barnes (TOR) establishes himself in Wright's (WAS) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Porzingis (WAS) legally contests VanVleet's (TOR) jump shot attempt.
Anunoby (TOR) cleanly blocks Wright's (WAS) shot attempt and any ensuing contact is incidental.
Siakam (TOR) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Anunoby (TOR) briefly has a hand placed around Porzingis's (WAS) hip, but he immediately removes it.
Porzingis (WAS) attempts to reach for the long rebound over Anunoby (TOR) and marginal contact occurs.  Anunoby does not undercut him or dislodge him from his rebounding position.
Beal (WAS) briefly gets a hand on the ball, but Anunoby (TOR) is quickly able to regain full control and make the pass.
Anunoby (TOR) gathers the ball and legally takes two steps.
Kispert (WAS) commits a take foul on Barnes (TOR).  The illegal contact occurs before Barnes begins his upward shooting motion.
Siakam (TOR) and Kuzma (WAS) briefly engage and disengage and Siakam does not extend into Kuzma to create space.
Porzingis (WAS) makes contact to Siakam's (TOR) arm that affects his SQBR at the basket.
